    {
      "name": "Capstone project - Blog website",
      "description": "This full-stack web application, built with Flask and Jinja2, includes key features such as secure user registration and login, post creation, and a commenting system for user interaction. The frontend is rendered using Jinja2 templates while form validation is handled using Flask-WTForms. The backend uses SQLAlchemy for robust database management. \nThe project is a great example of authentication, CRUD operations, and full-stack integration in Python.",
      "submodules": [
        {
